 14 Following the independence of South Soudan on 9 July 2011, and its admission as a United Nations 
</p>
<p>Member State on 14 July 2011, the Working Group has started reviewing the cases recorded under 
Sudan to determine whether these should be transferred to the records of South Soudan in accordance 
to the Working Group&#8217;s working methods. </p>


