Government transmitted information on all outstanding cases. The information provided 
was not considered sufficient to lead to their clarification. 
</p>
<p>620. In the second communication, dated 28 April 2011, the Government transmitted a copy 
of the Report of the Ombudsman of the Republic of Tajikistan on Human Rights for 2009-
</p><p>2010.  
</p>
<p>621. In the fourth communication, dated 11 July 2011, the Government retransmitted the 
information provided on 2 July 2011. </p>


<p>622. In the fifth communication, dated 22 August 2011, the Government replied positively 
to the Working Group&#8217;s request for a visit. 
</p>
